   <p>The value of churches in 1924 was $586,000 and parsonages $181,200. Balaries for 1924 were $62,151 and gifts to charity amounted to $31,354...Of 47 pastors in the service in 1924, 32 were born in Norway, 6 in Denmark, 2 in Sweden and 7 in America."</p>
